<% content_for :title, "Uses" %>
<% content_for :head do %>
  <%= meta_tags(title: "Uses", description: "Tools, gear, and software I use every day.") %>
<% end %>

<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">Uses</h1>

<div class="space-y-6 text-ink leading-relaxed">
  <p>A running list of tools and gear I use daily. Inspired by <a href="https://uses.tech" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">uses.tech</a>.</p>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Hardware</h2>
    <p><strong class="text-ink font-semibold">MacBook Pro 14" M3</strong> — main machine. Fast enough that I stopped thinking about performance.</p>
    <p><strong class="text-ink font-semibold">LG 27" 4K monitor</strong> — one external display, centered. I stopped using two monitors and never looked back.</p>
    <p><strong class="text-ink font-semibold">Sony WH-1000XM5</strong> — noise cancelling headphones for deep work.</p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Editor & Terminal</h2>
    <p><strong class="text-ink font-semibold">Neovim</strong> — primary editor. Took a month to set up properly, saves an hour a day.</p>
    <p><strong class="text-ink font-semibold">Ghostty</strong> — terminal. Fast, native, no configuration needed to look good.</p>
    <p><strong class="text-ink font-semibold">tmux</strong> — session management. One session per project.</p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Software</h2>
    <p><strong class="text-ink font-semibold">Arc</strong> — browser. Spaces keep client work and personal browsing separate.</p>
    <p><strong class="text-ink font-semibold">Linear</strong> — issue tracking for solo projects. Overkill but I like the keyboard shortcuts.</p>
    <p><strong class="text-ink font-semibold">Obsidian</strong> — notes and writing drafts before they become essays here.</p>
    <p><strong class="text-ink font-semibold">Postico</strong> — database GUI for when SQL in the terminal isn't enough.</p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Stack</h2>
    <p>Ruby on Rails, SQLite in production, deployed on a single Hetzner VPS via Kamal. This site is built the same way.</p>
  </div>
</div>
